{"_path":"/resident/r017","_dir":"resident","_draft":false,"_partial":false,"_locale":"","title":"讓流浪狗也能居有定所","description":null,"image":"/images/resident/r017-02.jpeg","sequence":17,"category":"環境保護","place":"A7重劃區","author":"社區網站","head":{"meta":[{"name":"keywords","content":""},{"name":"robots","content":""},{"name":"author","content":""},{"name":"copyright","content":"© 2024 "},{"name":"og:title","content":"社區網站-地方行政"}]},"publishedAt":"2024-08-10T00:00:00.000Z","toc":true,"body":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"讓流浪狗也能居有定所"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"讓流浪狗也能居有定所"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"a7-重劃區的流浪狗問題"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"A7 重劃區的流浪狗問題"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"A7 重劃區內仍有許多流浪狗, 在區域建案開發中 需要餵流浪狗尋求居所。 目前在 樂學路上樂學一路及樂學三路之間路段, 文化一路變二工地前 及 文桃路與南林路交匯處 會有善心人士大量投放食物。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"投放的食物包含飲水, 狗糧, 剩飯/菜 等等。 往往也帶來大量的蚊蠅。 造成區域環境極為惡劣。 也增加 A7 重劃區居民, 尤其是婦女, 幼兒遭受攻擊的隱患。 增加狂犬病, 及其他疫病傳播的風險。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"r017-03.jpeg","src":"/images/resident/r017-03.jpeg"},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"r017-04.jpeg","src":"/images/resident/r017-04.jpeg"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"桃園市現行流浪狗管理作業辦法"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"桃園市現行流浪狗管理作業辦法"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"桃園市發現流浪狗時，聯繫相關機構，以確保動物和人員的安全:"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"1959 "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://taw.tycg.gov.tw/X00_index.aspx"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"桃園市動物保護教育園區"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：電話：1959 或 03-332-6742"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"1999 市民專線： 撥打 1999，選擇動物保護相關選項，報告流浪狗的具體位置和狀況。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://animal.tycg.gov.tw/Default.aspx"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"桃園市動物保護防疫處"}]},{"type":"text","value":"： 該單位也負責流浪動物的管理與救援。"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://taw.tycg.gov.tw/X00_index.aspx"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"桃園市動物保護教育園區"}]},{"type":"text","value":" 提供服務包含"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"領養作業：如果你有領養意願，可以向動物保護教育園區詢問相關程序，參與領養。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"社區宣導：鼓勵社區居民參與流浪動物的救助和絕育活動，減少流浪狗問題。"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"希望里長能多舉辦 相關 活動, 包含邀請專業人士來社區宣導及舉辦以領養代替買賣！"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"防止在-a7-重劃區餵食流浪狗"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"防止在 A7 重劃區餵食流浪狗"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"廢棄物清理法"}]},{"type":"text","value":":\n如果餵食行為導致食物殘渣或垃圾留在公共場所，這可能會被視為違反《廢棄物清理法》，根據該法第 27 條，亂丟垃圾或未妥善處理垃圾的人可能會被處以罰款。違反者可能面臨新台幣 1,200 元至 6,000 元的罰款 ​。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"動物保護法"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：\n台灣的《動物保護法》強調對動物的保護和善待，並沒有明確禁止餵食流浪動物的條款。然而，根據第 5 條，飼主或照顧者有義務保持環境衛生，避免滋生病媒，影響公共衛生 ("},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/life/breakingnews/4764338","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"自由時報電子報"}]},{"type":"text","value":")。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"r017-01.jpeg","src":"/images/resident/r017-01.jpeg"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"eleme